{"tid":159443,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有時茶記收皮真係唔怪得人","createTime":"2017-03-17T04:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T04:42:45.000Z","uid":34489,"like":78,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e85e8b65fd05cbbc01b42fbf8c530eb5654cc49","tid":159443,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"開張幫襯到依家<br />\n一日難食過一日<br />\nD杯碟愈黎愈污遭<br />\n快餐夠膽死日日一樣 仲係咁加價<br />\n我係街市買個雙送飯平你10幾蚊又好食過你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b494b47b7e02bd954af204c041fb544ab1173696","tid":159443,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"港豬先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早餐叫正正常常，除左杯野飲<br />\nlunch、晚飯好似狗屎咁難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bede59776284a2fac1ec879533d564468271b942","tid":159443,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早餐叫正正常常，除左杯野飲<br />\nlunch、晚飯好似狗屎咁難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去連鎖俾貴幾蚊好過 唔洗食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f42d3ac35baf4df622e5f7aaefcbaf272bd7c7","tid":159443,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"AGGER CHING<br />\n得罪講句<br />\n大快活都屌打茶記＝。＝"},{"pid":"134da242676b8c