g src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff4d710c7e6df31f549375f105f1171b649d06e","tid":159443,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"永遠只食連鎖 菜記留番左膠食"},{"pid":"6742af828fbff41cb78e7ce8b1fea63297f6d421","tid":159443,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同意，至撚憎茶記</blockquote><br />\n本身樓下有間幾正 黑椒汁真係黑椒汁 蒜容汁真係蒜容汁<br />\nD野食又有獲氣 食牛面又唔會得兩塊冇味又咬唔到既垃圾<br />\n不過可惜執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好野通常好難做得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經成日幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d93317a2bbdaa7569bb6f477c2e9aab9b6edbd","tid":159443,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"謝西瓜你隻食屎狗 食芝士漢堡喇仆你個臭街"},{"pid":"51d11a50a9d1b0b8ded5c31f0ef282bddb1f088b","tid":159443,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:17:57.000Z","msg":"Hea到"},{"pid":"9bf2682db6f87794584e4aa7cc9eed5e11ffcf02","tid":159443,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c8e6e16649f0f91caf1e6f8ca94bebc0579877","tid":159443,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"污糟同埋態度差我已經唔會考慮喇"},{"pid":"da15cdec6dacdf5da347366b32bfecacd87c829c","tid":159443,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"啲人成日叫人多啲幫襯茶記 支持下佢哋<br />\n喂大佬呀，支持得落先得架 ，又污糟又難食，啲呀姐又無禮貌，我比錢入黎食野都要睇你面色?????"},{"pid":"bdc68afaf6de44b06d7a2cba53af781315eb8900","tid":159443,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲人成日叫人多啲幫襯茶記 支持下佢哋<br />\n喂大佬呀，支持得落先得架 ，又污糟又難食，啲呀姐又無禮貌，我比錢入黎食野都要睇你面色?????</blockquote><br />\n仲又貴，屌佢老母"},{"pid":"b4b16941ca1d972b31201ea6d819aab22776acc5","tid":159443,"uid":19272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:17:39.000Z","msg":"不如大家幫襯多啲真係有心做嘅茶記啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇心做個啲就出全力屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1eae53c5e29247ff2281d9a5c13e59aa0421558","tid":159443,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲人成日叫人多啲幫襯茶記 支持下佢哋<br />\n喂大佬呀，支持得落先得架 ，又污糟又難食，啲呀姐又無禮貌，我比錢入黎食野都要睇你面色?????</blockquote><br />\n仲又貴，屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n成撚日吹奏佢地，話咩本土特色，咁撚劣質嘅特色唔需要支持。"},{"pid":"c0c2c9b20501553c950aaa840e2a41af75390ae4","tid":159443,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"去過九龍冰室飲九紋龍沖既奶茶未"},{"pid":"63bf87b3a3246de247da668a522b21104b9eef6c","tid":159443,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"有腦都唔會去食茶記<br />\n啲租咁貴點會整到好野食比你<br />\n食材只會有咁差得咁差<br />\n華人開餐廳只係當生意 唔會擺個心落去做"},{"pid":"6d46573ee2f12a217d867ce22c77dd2638b1232a","tid":159443,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲人成日叫人多啲幫襯茶記 支持下佢哋<br />\n喂大佬呀，支持得落先得架 ，又污糟又難食，啲呀姐又無禮貌，我比錢入黎食野都要睇你面色?????</blockquote><br />\n仲又貴，屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n成撚日吹奏佢地，話咩本土特色，咁撚劣質嘅特色唔需要支持。</blockquote><br />\n我試過係茶記食揚州炒飯，炒飯入面竟然有兩支牙籤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩食咗兩啖就見到，真係好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec17d6b7b86374a45d6c78a1d12cef73f0c94f37","tid":159443,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"好彩我樓下間茶記幾高質下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9efa928eff050da6405a93827993f2e7822bc08","tid":159443,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"食碟星米，屌佢個碟油撚到，都唔知有無洗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3a232473dfcbbefca22d95cf527ce1cbc70747","tid":159443,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"有心個d 都汁哂"},{"pid":"166b96b6f754d5f24213d3a9e0ae39afc5fc5ee4","tid":159443,"uid":5813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有心個d 都汁哂</blockquote><br />\n好多好食又抵屌果d收哂皮，租金太貴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd7a0379a12e04d363dc26f019e30fb9ac88e19","tid":159443,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"港燦快去幫襯澳牛，九記牛腩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比侍應西面？唔緊要！排隊好耐？唔緊要！環境污糟？唔緊要！<br />\n最緊要果間係小店，小店嘅垃圾都好食過連鎖點嘅普通野食<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edea4d5bc4d0174f10e79c1fbdb5f9183c82bf48","tid":159443,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"我反而最憎環境<br />\n唔係要你五星級裝修<br />\n但大佬，紙箱周圍都係，地方又濕又臭，張檯又油喎<br />\n<br />\n啲啊伯最中意話後生仔要求多多/唔挨得<br />\n如果檔野係掂，我坐係條街食都肯<br />\n<br />\n2017年啦，服務差就服務差啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"d9d050047eb5b7fa9936fde44ce9e1596ce6fe76","tid":159443,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港燦快去幫襯澳牛，九記牛腩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比侍應西面？唔緊要！排隊好耐？唔緊要！環境污糟？唔緊要！<br />\n最緊要果間係小店，小店嘅垃圾都好食過連鎖點嘅普通野食<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北角x好運有老鼠咪又係要<br />\n排隊<br />\n<br />\n你唔食大把人排隊去食"},{"pid":"8e1c96f2cd5370c87a88f20df8d8c79ceace5111","tid":159443,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"老野阿叔先鐘意食茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知丫屌我條女平時問佢食乜竟然會答茶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0613258802178814229589fc9e53c1b44911d59c","tid":159443,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而最憎環境<br />\n唔係要你五星級裝修<br />\n但大佬，紙箱周圍都係，地方又濕又臭，張檯又油喎<br />\n<br />\n啲啊伯最中意話後生仔要求多多/唔挨得<br />\n如果檔野係掂，我坐係條街食都肯<br />\n<br />\n2017年啦，服務差就服務差啦⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n張檯油我最多唔掂 坐遠D<br />\n但係飲杯野個杯都好似冇洗過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35bf4e018fe61fa3783f8de8c5b1ce8a4e2e312","tid":159443,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而最憎環境<br />\n唔係要你五星級裝修<br />\n但大佬，紙箱周圍都係，地方又濕又臭，張檯又油喎<br />\n<br />\n啲啊伯最中意話後生仔要求多多/唔挨得<br />\n如果檔野係掂，我坐係條街食都肯<br />\n<br />\n2017年啦，服務差就服務差啦⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n張檯油我最多唔掂 坐遠D<br />\n但係飲杯野個杯都好似冇洗過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有油"},{"pid":"baeaf99b8ff7ab4cbba46484d6c822dc6509787d","tid":159443,"uid":2079,"like":0,"di